{"ja307:0.1":"Jataka ","ja307:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja307:0.3":"Kalingavagga ","ja307:0.4":"7. Palasajataka ","ja307:1.1":"“Acetanam brahmana assunantam, ","ja307:1.2":"Jano ajanantamimam palasam; ","ja307:1.3":"Araddhaviriyo dhuvam appamatto, ","ja307:1.4":"Sukhaseyyam pucchasi kissa hetu”. ","ja307:2.1":"“Dure suto ceva braha ca rukkho, ","ja307:2.2":"Dese thito bhutanivasarupo; ","ja307:2.3":"Tasma namassami imam palasam, ","ja307:2.4":"Ye cettha bhuta te dhanassa hetu”. ","ja307:3.1":"“So te karissami yathanubhavam, ","ja307:3.2":"Katannutam brahmana pekkhamano; ","ja307:3.3":"Kathanhi agamma satam sakase, ","ja307:3.4":"Moghani te assu pariphanditani. ","ja307:4.1":"Yo tindukarukkhassa paro pilakkho, ","ja307:4.2":"Parivarito pubbayanno ularo; ","ja307:4.3":"Tassesa mulasmim nidhi nikhato, ","ja307:4.4":"Adayado gaccha tam uddharahi”ti. ","ja307:5.1":"Palasajatakam sattamam. "}